DECEIVE→WARS→NATION/NATION→FAMINE→EARTHQUAKE→BIRTH_PAINS→PERSECUTION→THE_END→ABOMINATION→FLEE→GREAT_TRIBULATION→FALSE_SIGNS→LIGHTNING/RETURN→COSMIC_SHAKING→GATHERING. Unbroken chain; each symbol's context bag confirms the next link.

### ROLE SHIFTS:
- EARTHQUAKE in v7 = literal seismic events; in v29 = cosmic/heavenly shaking. Role shifts from sign to consummation.
- THE_END shifts from "not yet" (v6) to conditional fulfillment (v14) — the end is not a clock but a mission-completion marker.

### WHAT'S MISSING:
- BABYLON — not named but Isa13:10 (Babylon oracle) is the source for v29's cosmic language. Babylon's judgment vocabulary applied to this tribulation.
- FIRE — absent despite DAYS_OF_NOAH context (2Pet3:7 water→fire). The fire judgment is implicit but unstated in this section.
- MARRIAGE — absent until vv37-39 (Noah: marrying/giving in marriage). Missing from vv4-31 = the SLEEP/normalcy element deferred.
- OIL/VIRGIN/HARLOT — absent until ch25 parables. Separation symbols follow the roadmap.

### LANGUAGE-LAYER CONNECTIONS:
- H2256 chebel (cord+pain): Matt24:8 ōdin echoes the Hebrew double-meaning — covenant cord tightening = birth pangs. Visible only via Hebrew root.
- H1698 deber (pestilence) / H1697 dabar (word): Lk21:11 includes pestilences where Matt omits — the deber/dabar link (Word-withdrawal = death) operates beneath surface.
- G1996 episunago (v31) → G1997 episunagoge (2Th2:1): same compound root. Paul's "gathering to Him" IS this verse.

### INCIDENTAL IMPORTS:
- "Sabbath" (v20) — only in Matthew. Implies Torah-observant audience; concrete: gates closed on Sabbath, flight hindered. Also: Sabbath = REST, opposite of BIRTH_PAINS.
- "Rooftop" (v17) — flat-roof Judean architecture. Don't go down INTO house = flee immediately over rooftops toward city wall. Concrete survival instruction.
- "Winter" (v20) — wadis flood, Judean passes dangerous. Physical obstacle to mountain flight.
- "Four winds" (v31) — Isa11:12, Eze37:9. Technical term for total compass gathering; also breath/spirit dimension.
- "Great trumpet" (v31) — Isa27:13 + Lev25:9 (Jubilee trumpet). Ingathering = Jubilee = covenant restoration.

